00/extras/0e03abd1a2da517cf8d7281409ceb399.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/bdcb8a6895ba6a4b18c52c36b15aaa1d.avif?t=1656620686\" width=641 height=98 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A choice of characters to choose from at the start with more to unlock</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/099adc3b63ad0b5914f4cda40cdc7eb1.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An original <strong>atmospheric soundtrack</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1817200/extras/d10002183c99adb5b02976f5875a7f74.webp?t=1656620686\" width=282 height=43 /></span><br>A variety of unique <strong>arcade style minigames</strong> based on the main story. These feature:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Shoot the Skulls:</strong> Use a plant pot to fire a tennis ball at skulls <br><i>(Just a normal day at the office)</i><br></li><li> <strong>Skull Sweeper </strong>: Use your brain to move the skulls to the correct colours</li></ul>",
